com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution

Class SplineMotionSprPrimitive

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution.SPRPrimitive
      • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution.MotionSprPrimitive
        • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution.SplineMotionSprPrimitive

  • public class SplineMotionSprPrimitive
extends MotionSprPrimitive
    Primitive class for spline motion SPR which map each motion to a an own spline SPR.
    Also takes care about the compound event handling for spline segment events.
    Is always recoverable.
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
